&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is a full time locum post which has become available due to increased clinical demand in the Barnet West Locality, one of our four community mental health teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful applicant will primarily work out of the Redhill Clinic (main offices based at Springwell Centre).The post holder will have experience with the full spectrum of psychiatric morbidity. This post is based in a multidisciplinary setting and the post holder will work closely with all the members of the team (CPNs, Psychologists, Social Workers &amp; Graduate Mental Health Workers). There will also be the experience of conducting home visits.The care delivered is recovery-focused, placing emphasis on individuals’ strengths and goals for the future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*Strictly no agencies please&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameDr Gil KovacJob titleConsultant PsychiatristEmail addressgil.kovac@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
